    <h2>Endpoint: <code>GET /analytics/:activityID</code></h2>
    <p>The <code>/analytics/:activityID</code> route allows users to retrieve detailed analytics information for a specific activity. This route is essential for monitoring the performance and outcomes of activities created in the BugMaster system.</p>

    <h3>How to Use This Endpoint:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Send a <code>GET</code> request to <code>/analytics/:activityID</code>, replacing <code>:activityID</code> with the unique identifier of the activity.</li>
      <li>Ensure that the provided <code>activityID</code> corresponds to an existing activity in the system.</li>
      <li>The response will include both quantitative and qualitative analytics for the activity.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Parameters:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>activityID</strong>: Required. The unique identifier of the activity for which analytics are requested.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Successful Response Example:</h3>
    <pre>
{
  "activityID": "12345",
  "Inven!RAStdID": "6e4a34a7-13d4-4b9d-a7ab-dc6546781a98",
  "quantAnalytics": [
    { "name": "bugs_identified", "type": "integer", "value": 5 },
    { "name": "classification_accuracy", "type": "percentage", "value": 85 },
    { "name": "time_spent_per_bug", "type": "integer", "value": 10 }
  ],
  "qualAnalytics": [
    { "name": "documentation_quality", "type": "text/plain", "value": "Good" },
    { "name": "access_to_test_environment", "type": "boolean", "value": true }
  ]
}
    </pre>

    <div class="example">
      <strong>Example Request Using HTTPie:</strong>
      <pre>
http GET https://bugmaster.onrender.com/analytics/12345
      </pre>
    </div>

    <h3>Error Handling:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>400 Bad Request:</strong> If the <code>activityID</code> is missing or invalid.
        <pre>
{
  "message": "Activity ID is required."
}
        </pre>
      </li>
      <li><strong>404 Not Found:</strong> If the activity is not found in the system.
        <pre>
{
  "message": "Activity not available."
}
        </pre>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Purpose of the Endpoint:</h3>
    <p>The purpose of this route is to provide a comprehensive set of analytics for an activity. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>QuantAnalytics:</strong> Quantitative data such as the number of bugs identified, classification accuracy, and time spent per bug.</li>
      <li><strong>QualAnalytics:</strong> Qualitative data such as documentation quality and access to the test environment.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Notes:</h3>
    <p>This endpoint is part of BugMaster's monitoring and evaluation system. It is subject to future enhancements to include additional data and greater flexibility in reporting analytics.</p>
